{
  "stem": "6900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to dig it in the earth under the latrine, and that's why my son has it now, because the day we were going-- evacuated from there, I picked it up and took it with us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no hygiene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we-- at 12 o'clock, they used to-- the SS women used to take us to the toilets.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were toilets there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to take the water-- try and take the water out of the cistern on top.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was old-fashioned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to pull a chain and get the water, and we used to wipe our faces.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of us tried to drink the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had nothing to drink all the time we were down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What did the women--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "12 Hours we were down there every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The strangest thing was when we were already in a-- in a Belsen, before we went, they stopped completely, which was a good thing for us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stopped completely, completely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never thought about it at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Relieved, but that was all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only our group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- only--  only our group of women worked in that particular place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The men were digging the salt in a different area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we used to see them in passing going to the shaft-- you know, to go up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to-- one of them or the other would whisper something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at a certain time, they whispered, they're loosing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know whether to trust them or believe them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We never spoke to them, because we were afraid, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then one morning-- and when we came back from the shaft, I will tell you, they gave us two pieces, two small pieces, of ersatz bread and a cup of ersatz coffee.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
